{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 17341, "create_time": 1640365136, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "答案：当然不是政策制度者的孩子", "timestamp": 1640365136}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 17350, "create_time": 1640365646, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "保持原来的高升学率并不能凭空增加就业岗位", "timestamp": 1640365646}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 17351, "create_time": 1640365652, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "我只有一个问题，十年后当每年的初中毕业生从接近两千万降到不足一千万之后，还会不会坚持1：1的普职分流比，到时候是削减普高和大学的招生名额甚至关停大半普高和大学，还是把职高关掉像台湾一样接近100%的人上大学", "timestamp": 1640365652}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 17356, "create_time": 1640365786, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re Bob: 我认为人口红利消失只会导致更加供养不起脱产者", "timestamp": 1640365786}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 17357, "create_time": 1640365830, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "Re Bob: 很显然出生人口减少的速度出乎了高层的预料，我相信这个问题他们也没有答案。毕竟原来他们还在做着放开二胎之后年出生人口就奔着三千万以上、人口红利源源不断、永远维持世界工厂的春秋大梦，当现实就是迅速而疯狂地打烂了海专精的脸", "timestamp": 1640365830}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 17358, "create_time": 1640365907, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Bob: 十年后有可能中国的科技真正上去了，需要人投入高新产业。那时候，学生的人均教育资源也会比我们多很多，master成为大学毕业标准", "timestamp": 1640365907}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 17359, "create_time": 1640366075, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "他们能真正享受高等教育的乐趣，学自己想学的有前途和希望的专业", "timestamp": 1640366075}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 17360, "create_time": 1640366218, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "人少一些倒好，竞争会少一些", "timestamp": 1640366218}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 17362, "create_time": 1640366396, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "Re 洞主: 学历本身其实仅仅只是供雇主参考的信号而已，如果所有人都有本科学历，那本科学历就会像大专、中专学历一样不值钱。", "timestamp": 1640366396}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 17364, "create_time": 1640366637, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "Re 洞主: 说白了，问题根本不在于普职分流，而是中国对于低技能劳动者的保障实在太差，职高的学生还会被以实习的名义当成廉价劳动力送给工厂白嫖，简直难以想象。当然人口的减少，会增加劳动力的稀缺性，以后三十五岁危机可能会被永远终结。现在很多工厂根本不要五十岁以上的人，以后也不会有挑三拣四的资本", "timestamp": 1640366637}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 17466, "create_time": 1640404777, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 3, "text": "[tmp]\n普职分流是多少年的老政策了", "timestamp": 1640404777}], "create_time": 1640365059, "cw": "社会问题", "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1640404777, "likenum": 4, "n_attentions": 4, "n_comments": 11, "pid": 5790, "poll": null, "reply": 11, "text": "国家规定了初中之后技专科和高中分流1:1\n国家减掉了教培机构，减掉了小学一二年级的作业和考试\n那么，你猜哪些阶层的孩子会去充实技校，失去上高中的机会呢？", "timestamp": 1640365059}}